## Voicing Reversal (Architectural)

Western Armenian has **reversed voicing** from letter appearance:

| Grapheme | WA Phone | WA Roman | EA (WRONG) | Example |
|----------|----------|----------|------------|---------|
| բ | /p/ | p | b | բան = pan (not ban) |
| պ | /b/ | b | p | պետք = bedk (not petik) |
| դ | /t/ | t | d | դուռ = toor (not door) |
| տ | /d/ | d | t | տուն = doon (not toon) |
| գ | /k/ | k | g | գիտ = keed (not geed) |
| կ | /g/ | g | k | կտուր = g'door (not kdoor) |
| ճ | /dʒ/ | j | ch | ճ = j as in "job" |
| ջ | /tʃ/ | ch | j | ջուր = choor (not jour) |
| ձ | /ts/ | ts | dz | ձայն = tsayn (not dzayn) |
| ծ | /dz/ | dz | ts | ծանի = dzani (not tsani) |

