## Mandatory Checklist Before Any Armenian Output

- [ ] Did I verify **every single character** in each word against the WA tables above (letter-by-letter)?
- [ ] Did I consult docs/armenian_language_guids?
- [ ] Did I use WA voicing (բ=p, պ=b, դ=t, տ=d, գ=k, կ=g)?
- [ ] Did I use ջ=ch, ճ=j, ձ=ts, ծ=dz (never the EA swap)?
- [ ] Did I use ը=u (never e), թ=t (never th)?
- [ ] Did I use classical orthography (իւ not reformed)?
- [ ] Did I use -եան = -ian (never -ean) in names? (Mekhitarian, not Mekhitarean)
- [ ] Did I insert unwritten "u" (schwa) between consonants where WA pronunciation has it? (e.g. Montureal)
- [ ] Did I use b (never P) for պ in every word? (Beyrout, Bosdon, Haleb)
- [ ] Did I use d (never T) for Տ? (Daniel)
- [ ] Did I re-scan the output for any EA default (e.g. "mej" for մէջ, "jour" for ջուր, "P" for պ)? If yes, correct to WA.
